CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Soul and Vibe Interactive Inc publish games, interactive books, and downloadable/streamable music for digital devices. The company develops, publishes, and distributes interactive entertainment games and interactive books for video game consoles, mobile and augmented reality/wearable tech devices, personal computers, and social media platforms. It develops, publishes, and distribute music for play on digital devices through downloadable/streamable channels that include Apple Music, iTunes, Google Play, Amazon, Deezer, YouTube Music, Beats/MediaNet, and Microsoft Groove.
